                            <comment id="17033603" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 10 Feb 2020 13:41:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;getProcessors is intended for read-only - not for mutation. so its #1 and its mostly used for testing. And its use can be replaced with org.apache.camel.Navigate, so we can remove the method and use Navigate instead. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
